strings: <se_high>*: <IF_SOLO>Hello visitors, do you want to relax in our church?<ELSE_NOT_SOLO>Hello travellers, would you like to rest in our temple?<ENDIF_SOLO>
<se_high>*: Since today is a religious holiday, we always get small gifts for our families. But today we are free.
<se_high>*: the way you want it a few bones be careful
<se_high>*: The service is very basic, but I think you will have a lot of fun.
<se_high>*: I want to earn 10 gold coins...
<se_high>*: Honey, I don't think you can afford it.
<se_high>*: I can't bear to get up, but I wish you a good journey.
